These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, fisherman
1. the firefighter is on the far left##1
2. the analyst is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | firefighter | fisherman | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, librarian, nurse
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the pilot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | pilot | librarian | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, camping, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | hiking | camping | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
