.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, soy-milk
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | juice | milk | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, tram, motorbike
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | motorbike | tram | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, drama, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | family | drama |

 #################################

 
